LASALLE BANK N.A. as Trustee FOR the MLMI TRUST SERIES 2006-AHL1, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Kelley A. SPEAR, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
William R. Spear and Rjm Acquisitions LLC, Defendants. C-810 Sept. Term 2017
080345 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 17, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005377-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
